data.description: Welcome to beautiful home in the Ballentrae neighborhood. Enjoy the open concept living and kitchen areas with tons of natural light, making this the perfect central hub of the home. The dream kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and ample cabinets - a perfect space to unleash your culinary creativity. The generously sized master suite is a true oasis, featuring a walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom with a luxurious soaking tub and separate shower. Upstairs the den and 3 bedrooms offer space for family, guests, or a home office or fitness room to suit your needs. Step outside to the private backyard complete with a spacious covered patio for alfresco dining, a manicured lawn for outdoor play, a fenced pet area and no neighbors behind you. Enjoy this award-winning neighborhood with pool, clubhouse, workout facility and access to a gorgeous golf course. See this perfect blend of relaxation in a vibrant community.
